
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-barnes-cfrg-hpke-01.txt'>
    <title>"Hybrid Public Key Encryption", Richard Barnes, Karthikeyan Bhargavan</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-barnes-cfrg-hpke-01.txt</link>
    <description>This document describes a scheme for hybrid public-key encryption (HPKE).  This scheme provides authenticated public key encryption of arbitrary-sized plaintexts for a recipient public key.  HPKE works for any Diffie-Hellman group and has a strong security proof.  We provide instantiations of the scheme using standard and efficient primitives.</description>
    <dc:date>2019-03-11T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
